[SN]TITLE[SN]
NHS Borders seeks new medical director

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
NHS Borders is seeking a new medical director less than a year after the last appointment to the post.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Andrew Murray is moving to NHS Forth Valley in February next year after 11 months with the south east Scotland health board.
NHS Borders said it was looking for an "inspirational and committed medical leader" to take his place.
